result.name: Green Waffle Diner

reviews.text: How is this a 4 star plus?!!it use to be okay when it first opened but it’s gone downhill substantially. Considering how easy it is to make an English breakfast, you couldn’t mess it up any worse. Try for yourself if you don’t believe me. Plenty of better places in the neighbourhood.
Great food and good coffee. Service ain't half bad either!

This was good for breakfast. We had some nice waffles and a breakfast skillet. There were vegi options and a lot of gluten free items. The coffee I had was decent enough.

My only complaint would be that It was a little expensive for what we got.

One of the best meals I've had in a while.  Passion fruit soft drink was to die for.   Great customer service with great care placed to cater for people with allergies.  Including skillets which were amazing.   Great ambience and good staff.

I didn't expect there is a place like the Green Waffle around Central. Even I've been working here for 4 months haha. Very very great quality of food. The photo below is the omelette of your choice. I picked smoked salmon, onion and cheese. You know what happened?? I have to ate first haha. So hungry that day.

They charges at a fair price. I can't wait to try some other food there. The risotto and potatoes also quite good. Just that I prefer high protein diet myself lol. 

Back to work now.

reviews.text: Superleckeres Essen, entspannte Atmosphäre. Die Bedienung ist freundlich und aufmerksam. Es gibt schöne große Tische und bequeme Sitzecken, die sich sehr gut zum Arbeiten am Laptop anbieten. Ich hatte die Berry Waffle mit Vanilleeis und war sehr zufrieden damit. Der Preis von 84 Hongkong-Dollar war auch absolut in Ordnung.

- ¡Qué pena pero tengo que cambiar mi puntuación de 5 estrellas y bajarlo a una porque hemos repetido pero el segundo día ha sido un desastre! En la cena todo mal porque han tardado 40 minutos en traer un plato de dos y se ha quedado fría la mitad de la cena! Y no bajo mi puntuación por eso. Es por el trato y por lo mal que lo han gestionado. La comida estaba buena, pero si el trato es malo la comida tiene que ser excelente para que no lo notes.

Opción excelente para celíacos que vengan a Hong Kong de visita y situado muy cerca de las famosas escaleras cubiertas.
